2013-10-25 Satoshi Konno <skonno@cybergarage.org>
	* v.2.0
	* Changed to use uHTTP for C++ v0.6.
	* Changed to use boost::testunit instead of cppunit.
	* Removed header and source files for UPnP/AV
	* Removed WIN32 and T-Engine projects.
	* Removed Node::toUnicodeString() and XML::Local2Unicode().
	* Fixed Node::setAttribute() to set the specified value when the attribute is null.
	* Fixed Service::getSCPDNode() to return null when the URLBase and the Location are null. 
	* Changed libxml2 parser using the latest functions.
	* Fixed a bug convertToCLinkFormat of libxml2 parser.
	* Improved Socket::connect() to ignore SIGPIPE on MacOSX 10.7.
	* Added Device::hasDeviceData().
	* Fixed Device::getLeaseTime() not to abort when the device data is null.

